(418, 1, 'Admark Ceramic', 'Admark Ceramic Industries Pvt. Ltd.\r\nManufacturer of Digital Wall Tiles\r\nJetper Road - Bela,\r\nMorbi-363642- Gujarat India', 'Morbi', 'Gujarat', 363642, 'http://admarkceramic.com/', '', '+919099986966', '', '', '', 'info@admarkceramic.com', '', '', '', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.way.admarkceramic', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/admark-ceramic/id878918227?ls=1&mt=8https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/admark-ceramic/id878918227?ls=1&mt=8', 'Welcome to a World limited only by your imagination, creativity and innovative skills. A World where you can spread your wings and find a myraid ways to express your wildest designs fantasies&nbsp;<br><br>The world of Admark Ceramic Industries Pvt. Ltd, pioneers and one of the largest selling designer Wall Tiles Company.In the following pages you will be introduced to the latest collection of digital Wall tiles the rarest, most unconventional and imaginative designer Wall Tiles youd have ever set up your eyes on.&nbsp;<br><br>"the first among the equals" brand that rolls out through the state-of-the-art Italian machines which are operated under the supervision of Italian technology team.', '1402815927.png', '', 1, 0, 0, 0),
(419, 1, 'Arido Ceramic', '8-A, National Highway, Matel Road,\r\nWankaner (Gujarat) INDIA.', 'Wankaner', 'Gujarat', 363642, 'http://aridoceramic.com/', '', '+91-8758777778', '', '+91-8758777779', '', 'info@aridoceramic.com', '', '70.983432', '22.726751', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.way.aridoceramic', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/arido-ceramic/id821451518?ls=1&mt=8', '<div><div><h3>OUR&nbsp;COMPANY</h3><ul><li><div><span>ARIDO CERAMIC is a technologically sound largest digital wall tiles exporter &amp; manufacturing company. The company engaged to manufacturing tiles of 12 x 24 inch. The firm is a fast-growing, highly respected company that seeks to be the preferred, trusted and successful long-term partner for its stakeholders - clients, partners, associates and its employees. Aridos aim is to add tangible value to the business of its clients in every engagement established in 2014. The manufacturing capacity of the is 7000 boxes per day.&nbsp;<br><br>ARIDO does this through innovation and efficient execution - steeled by the principle of consistency.</span></div></li></ul></div><div><br></div><div></div></div><div><div><h3>OUR&nbsp;MISSION</h3><ul><li><div><span>We will strive to attain leadership in the markets we choose to serve by creating innovative and differentiated products that would be moulded with impeccable quality.&nbsp;<br><br>We will achieve this mission:&nbsp;<br>By being driven by market need&nbsp;<br>By innovating<br>By improving continuously&nbsp;<br>By staying focused&nbsp;<br>By hiring and retaining talented and successful employees&nbsp;<br>By being fair and ethical at all times&nbsp;<br>By reviewing our progress through honest feedback from our employees.</span></div></li></ul></div><div><h3>OUR&nbsp;VISION</h3><ul><li><div>To be the preferred, successful and trusted long-term partners to all our stakeholders â€“ clientâ€™s, associates and our employees. For this to be possible, we will be viable and relevant through practical innovation and a continuous focus on efficiency and consistency.</div></li></ul></div><div><h3>BUSINESS&nbsp;PHILOSOPHY</h3><ul><li><div><span>To respond to the various needs of society, we are constantly tackling research and development on new technologies and products and endeavor to provide ever more superior products to the world.&nbsp;<br><br>We will continue to address the requirements of the world in a new era, such as technical innovation, development of infrastructure, globalization and a heightened awareness of the environmental protection.&nbsp;<br><br>We work on a market-driven corporate philosophy. Transparency with our clients and potential clients is our understanding of corporate success.</span></div></li></ul></div></div>', '1402820355.png', '', 1, 0, 0, 0),
